001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;

003import com.netflix.graphql.dgs.client.codegen.BaseSubProjectionNode;
004import java.lang.String;
005import java.util.ArrayList;
006import java.util.List;
007
008public class AssetProjection<PARENT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>, ROOT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>> extends BaseSubProjectionNode<PARENT, ROOT> {
009  public AssetProjection(PARENT parent, ROOT root) {
010    super(parent, root, java.util.Optional.of("Asset"));
011  }
012
013  public AssetSourceProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> sources() {
014     AssetSourceProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new AssetSourceProjection<>(this, getRoot());
015     getFields().put("sources", projection);
016     return projection;
017  }
018
019  public LocalizedStringProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> nameAllLocales() {
020     LocalizedStringProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new LocalizedStringProjection<>(this, getRoot());
021     getFields().put("nameAllLocales", projection);
022     return projection;
023  }
024
025  public LocalizedStringProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> descriptionAllLocales() {
026     LocalizedStringProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new LocalizedStringProjection<>(this, getRoot());
027     getFields().put("descriptionAllLocales", projection);
028     return projection;
029  }
030
031  public CustomFieldsTypeProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> custom() {
032     CustomFieldsTypeProjection<AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new CustomFieldsTypeProjection<>(this, getRoot());
033     getFields().put("custom", projection);
034     return projection;

036
037  public AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT> id() {
038    getFields().put("id", null);
039    return this;
040  }
041
042  public AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT> key() {

045  }
046

048    getFields().put("name", null);
049    return this;
050  }
051
052  public AssetProjection name(String locale, List<String> acceptLanguage) {
053    getFields().put("name", null);
054    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("name", k -> new ArrayList<>());
055    InputArgument localeArg = new InputArgument("locale", locale);
056    getInputArguments().get("name").add(localeArg);
057    InputArgument acceptLanguageArg = new InputArgument("acceptLanguage", acceptLanguage);
058    getInputArguments().get("name").add(acceptLanguageArg);
059    return this;
060  }
061
062  public AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT> description() {
063    getFields().put("description", null);
064    return this;
065  }
066
067  public AssetProjection description(String locale, List<String> acceptLanguage) {
068    getFields().put("description", null);
069    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("description", k -> new ArrayList<>());
070    InputArgument localeArg = new InputArgument("locale", locale);
071    getInputArguments().get("description").add(localeArg);
072    InputArgument acceptLanguageArg = new InputArgument("acceptLanguage", acceptLanguage);
073    getInputArguments().get("description").add(acceptLanguageArg);
074    return this;
075  }
076
077  public AssetProjection<PARENT, ROOT> tags() {
